By generaon 20 nearly all trials had found the local opmal soluon. These

The Nanosaur had many hardware issues due to the plasc easily wearing
down, parcularly round the motors where the most heat was given out.
The tracks were replaced by wheels to combat this. The algorithm in itself
worked by nding simple routes without crashing.
Going forward, having a cheap small robot would allow other researchers in
the AI group to build more and use them to invesgate swarm navigaon
where dierent robots explore dierent parts of an environment and com-
pare their informaon.
